=== Emerge ===

{{Emerge|app-portage/cfg-update}}

== Configuration ==

Configuration is done through {{Path|/etc/cfg-update.conf}}.  The most common option users need to change is the <var>MERGE_TOOL</var> option to the preferred merge tool of the system.  Supported tools include meld, xxdiff, kdiff3, gvimdiff, tkdiff, vimdiff, sdiff and imediff2.

